{"tid":2063866,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普稱美軍不是世界警察　不是要重建海外國家","createTime":"2020-06-14T10:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T10:58:08.000Z","uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9c667016aa35c0cf8a6f154c925178d62a0c9a6d","tid":2063866,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T10:52:49.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普強調，美國軍隊不是世界警察，職責不是重建海外國家。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在西點軍校，向1100多名陸軍畢業學員演講。他表示，美軍不是去解決很多甚至從未聽說過的遙遠土地上的歷史衝突，而是保衛美國的國家安全，如果國民受到威脅，美軍將毫不猶疑行動，他又表示，美國正在恢復根本原則，終止無休止戰爭的時代，取而代之是重新將重點，明確放在保衛美國的關鍵利益上。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又表示，為了重新建設美國軍隊，他領導的政府已經投入超過兩萬億美元，購置新型艦艇、轟炸機、數百架軍用直升機、戰鬥機、新式坦克和導彈等，並研制超高音速的導彈，還成立了太空軍，目的就是確保美國軍隊擁有世界上最好的裝備與科技，繼續是世界上最強大的軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1531942_1_L_20200614063724.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1531942_1_L_20200614063724.jpg&h=beb6a0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531942-20200614.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531942-20200614.htm&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJr1zpTq0bGO0w7tnLPpoXkc%3D&h=5444e3ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531942-20200614.htm&h=9d4caff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531942-20200614.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c31cad979eb3f61861b91de9cb4e1b73c9a1cfd0","tid":2063866,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"打尻中國就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e39361c66d5b204717d3bf73ed9197bb197edd","tid":2063866,"uid":107656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"統一地球"},{"pid":"ee54da1189df880c2ed584b0347aa7214416c161","tid":2063866,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06